Class Examinator

  • java.lang.Object
    • categorize.Examinator

  • public class Examinator
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used to do some operations on the AST that we use to determinate which is the likely cause for a nonconformance.
    Author:
    Alysson Milanez and Dennis Sousa.
